dc_description_s: This data represents trails for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in 2024. [Milwaukee County recreational trail dataset compiled from a variety of sources and reviewed with latest aerial imagery. Trails shown include existing, proposed, county, state and municipal owned, for public access. Trails types include multiuse, hike, mountain biking, water and seasonal.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data-mclio.hub.arcgis.com/
